In this important talk, Joshua Vial of the Enspiral 'ethical entrepreneurial coalition' introduces the idea of 'capped investments'. This would guarantee a maximum amount of return for investors, after which the funded infrastructure would be donated to the commons, and the investors thanked for their donation to the commons.


